rest_of_day_open: I experienced a setback recently, but I am starting to recover and get myself going again. I think the weekend and next week will be better than the last 10 days have been. I hope to continue job hunting and to get my other projects working. Also a haircut! At the moment I am scaring small children.
critical_positive: He was easy to talk to, and I know that I can pretty much talk to anyone. It helps that we had some things in common, such as a distaste for Trump and agreement about certain aspects of the corona situation. I could see how we both carefully approached these topics, to prevent us getting into difficult territory in case we were actually not aligned on these issues. I have found this to be the only way to talk to strangers safely these days.
critical_negative: I sometimes have trouble with words these days, and I noticed some of that happening for me. Also, there was one area of conversation I was uncomfortable with, because I am not working and don’t entirely know what’s next. So I had to dissemble a bit when that came up. I think everything else worked fine.

rest_of_day_open: I see the rest of my week being relaxed without too much stress. I will spend time with my family and do a variety of activities with them. It will be positive and I will be happy to have the time to spend with them. My stress level will be low as it has been that way lately.
critical_positive: We were both relaxed and open to having the conversation. The topics we discussed came freely without much effort to move onto a new topic. We both were in good moods and friendly with each other with no expectations of how the conversation was going to go. There was no stress to the topics or our discussions.
critical_negative: The conversation could have had a better picture quality on her end as she was using a cam that was to close to her and I saw her eyes mainly throughout our session. I did not have any technical difficulties on my end, and the video was smooth and seamless. Audio quality was great throughout.
